headline: Sunshine Health Announces the Appointment of Charlene Zein as President and CEO
summary: Sunshine Health, Florida's largest managed care organization and a Centene Corporation company (NYSE: CNC), announced today Charlene Zein has been named Plan President and Chief Executive Officer, effective Nov. 3, 2024.
